window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Legendary healers can save cities from the brink of death with a word, but warriors can destroy them just as quickly. Ren will become both.</b></p> <p>Reincarnated into a world of magic and monsters, Ren gets a chance to live again. In a world where everyone awakens a single magical core, Ren discovers something impossible inside his soul: two. One a mana-bound healer, the other a warrior that wields the shadows.</p> <p>But power comes at a cost. Ren’s unique abilities come with powerful enemies and strange mysteries. Guilds, demons, and kingdoms scheme as an era of change comes to the new world, dragging him into a bloody mess.</p> <p>Fortunately, it turns out he thrives with his life on the line. Ren will walk through fire and drown in poison if that’s what it takes to grow his power.</p> <p>What doesn’t kill Ren makes him stronger, and healers are very hard to kill.</p> <p><i>Perfect for fans of The Beginning After the End, The Primal Hunter, and 1% Lifesteal!</i></p>"; 
